## Overview

This is an MCP (Model Context Protocol) server built with Rust using the [rmcp](https://github.com/anthropics/rmcp) SDK.

## Prerequisites

- Rust 1.70 or higher
- Cargo

## Installation

```bash
# Build the project
cargo build --release
```

## Running the Server

<% if (transport === 'stdio') { %>
